This repository contains the code for a simple and responsive News Landing Page built using HTML and CSS. 
The landing page displays featured news, breaking news, and includes a subscription form for newsletter sign-ups. 
The page is designed with modern web standards and includes basic styling for responsiveness.

Features
  Responsive grid layout for featured news articles.
  Horizontal scrolling breaking news ticker.
  Email subscription form.
  Modern and clean design.
  Smooth scrolling effect for anchor links.
  Optimized for mobile view with media queries.

Open the Landing.html file in any modern web browser to view the page.
The layout is responsive and adjusts based on screen size. Resize the browser window or open the page on a mobile device to test responsiveness

